\n<br />\n即係人民好多都係怕左佢<br />\n<br />\n所以佢既弱點就係當人民慘到一個點<br />\n<br />\n或者人民發現有能力打底佢既時候<br />\n<br />\n就有機會"},{"pid":"3ec2e1baf1f305a778c9e1b86a4475b15119a9c9","tid":1417654,"uid":272202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:36:51.000Z","msg":"諗唔到計 唯有列少少我對於共產黨嘅印象<br />\n1.極權統治<br />\n逆佢者死，極依賴高壓手段（評會評分制度，網警，打壓維權律師，新疆集中營）去維穩。<br />\n2.以經濟起飛自稱強國（第三世界國家）<br />\n如題，身為「強國」但唔負「強國」責任，有咩環保嘢就話自己係「第三世界國家」。<br />\n大部分人民都引以為傲，成日以為有錢就大曬，人家唔妥佢就係葡萄佢。<br />\n3.黨員數量多，核心官員大部分都係外國國藉/家屬係外國國藉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6f19936224bcea5950071ee3ca44975c7452dc0","tid":1417654,"uid":275634,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:38:03.000Z","msg":"驚內地人知道真相<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果hack 左成個微博你估有咩事發生<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c33d3176b68d287bf630e132e62dfe1c464078e","tid":1417654,"uid":232237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:45:31.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"c7bd490de9030b0af5291c6b865085d5c74395d8","tid":1417654,"uid":36089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:46:15.000Z","msg":"求求大家，盡快去換美元現鈔！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1417102\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1417102</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"533831a5cf38006815fe2a9d6fd340d31f4649c2","tid":1417654,"uid":272202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6f19936224bcea5950071ee3ca44975c7452dc0","tid":1417654,"uid":275634,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:38:03.000Z","msg":"驚內地人知道真相<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果hack 左成個微博你估有咩事發生<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:46:31.000Z","msg":"有啲內地人就算知都係扮傻<br />\n就算hack咗微博 佢地都只會話「港燦滾出微博」<br />\n佢地係70%驚共產黨+30%真蠢<br />\n我覺得只要有共同目標（例如三峽冧咗又冇做好救災）<br />\n夠多人有決心去對抗共產黨<br />\n啲人就會跟住做 好似帝吧嗰萬幾個撚屌咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但就係因為咁 所以佢地今時今日仲係做緊共產黨嘅奴隸<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a16422a1e2fb83dc5254fb3dddb60f17c23d6688","tid":1417654,"uid":141736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:48:47.000Z","msg":"我知道，但我之前講完冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6af1bca678dea2b370a0c2788ba4